{"tid":884023,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁國雄：退聯後抗爭無以為繼！仇思達只係識撥冷水，幾時先肯自己抗爭俾人睇下？收皮啦！","createTime":"2018-10-31T09:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T10:14:22.000Z","uid":49388,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1812b4adb055e9692e77fc0e436f7c0fdf7a7a7","tid":884023,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"1. 本土派在退聯後抗爭無以為繼<br />\n<br />\n2.主張勇武抗爭既馮敬恩都已經認錯知哀<br />\n<br />\n3.仇思達永遠只係識係抗爭者背後撥冷水，叫人唔好投黃雅文，港大有抗者佢又屌，但仇思達自己又做過D乜呢？一個連俾黃洋達都恰到懶尿既人，收皮啦，收呀！收皮呀！！！叫人退聯後做過D乜呀？去書展食熱狗抗爭呀？搞壇野黎睇下得唔得呀？！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gj3WHY_rMfA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgj3WHY_rMfA&d=FwYAA6jDIqA0QZLQKYkRCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=66848562\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gj3WHY_rMfA</a>"},{"pid":"a93abdf10719dba94ca1c0555794525f57901d0c","tid":884023,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0bb0a488b67fe70560d454f26cd1f30c2c8c5a","tid":884023,"uid":159990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"幾分幾秒"},{"pid":"0ad37d4dd4ded199f24bc2b37d14194ffaab8971","tid":884023,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"益友駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae0707f9f895bf8fd47bf37b94c11c38f1882e8","tid":884023,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"已經分唔清正評負皮係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}